.TH "pwm_capture" 9 "pwm_capture" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pwm_capture \- capture and report a PWM signal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pwm_capture
.BI "(struct pwm_device *pwm "  ","
.BI "struct pwm_capture *result "  ","
.BI "unsigned long timeout "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pwm" 12
PWM device
.IP "result" 12
structure to fill with capture result
.IP "timeout" 12
time to wait, in milliseconds, before giving up on capture
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or a negative error code on failure.
